    {
      "role": "user",
      "content": "when you say \"constrained by geopolitical reality,\" does that mean the criticisms of the Security Council—like how certain countries have way too much power to just block everything—are actually valid, or is that just an excuse for why the UN can't do its job?",
      "source": "evaluator"
